					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Jaheira's youngest daughter is practicing with a sword outside the front door - she's demanding, inquisitive and insistent in a way you would imagine a younger Jaheira might have been.\r\n\r\nThe kids are there to give little prompts to how to find the note that allows them to persuade the adult kids to stay. This one points the player to the hidden basement, and should give a hint that Harpers come and go."
				}
